title: Massage for Reflexology with Melanie Blanchard x264 aac MP4
description:
Soothe away the pains and tensions of those around you with this ancient method. Reflexology on the sloes of the feet is an ancient science which has been recognised for thousands of years, and which developed into its present from during the 1930s.

It considers the feet as the "mirrors of the body" and each organ, gland or part of the human body corresponds to an area or zone of the foot, known as the reflex zone.

This program features Melanie Blanchard, who is a reflexologist and also practices Shiatsu on patients in the sitting position.

Includes:

Demonstration
The different systems of the human body
Auto-massage
Thai reflexology
Hand massage
